### 1. 회원별 계좌 목록 조회
# Auth.http의 로그인 후 발급된 토큰 필요
# @name getAccounts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/member/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

> {% client.global.set("withdraw_account_id", response.body.data[0].id); %}

### 2. 특정 계좌 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/{{withdraw_account_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
